[package]
name = "openfpga-instance-packager"
version = "0.3.1"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
name = "instance_packager"
path = "src/lib.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "openfpga_instance_packager"
path = "src/bin.rs"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.91"
glob = "0.3.1"
question = "0.2.2"
walkdir = "2.3.2"
tempfile = "3.3.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.152"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.1.4"
features = ["derive"]
